  <brief_title>A Comparison of the Flex-it® to the GlideRite® Stylet for GlideScope® in Simulated Difficult Intubations.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Comparison of the Flex-it® Articulating Stylet to the GlideRite® Rigid Stylet for Orotracheal Intubation Using the GlideScope® in Simulated Difficult Intubations. A Double Blinded Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
